  "description": "<p>When after-dark adventures happen, this mega-bright and feature-rich headlamp lights the way. Updated with an internal rechargeable battery, the Spot 400-R keeps nearly every feature that has made the Spot one of Black Diamond\u2019s most successful headlamps, in fact the only feature you lose is having to replace the batteries. For 2022 Black Diamond releases their R series, adding a rechargeable option to many of their most popular models. Having an easy to recharge headlamp makes \u201cgood enough\u201d batteries a thing of the past.</p><ul><li>Smooth dimming feature lets you dial in the perfect brightness</li><li>PowerTap\u2122 feature on the housing takes you from any brightness mode to full power with a single tap. Tap it again to return lighting level</li><li>6 modes include bright white proximity, bright white distance, dimming, strobe, red proximity and red strobe</li><li>Charges easily via micro-USB, going from empty to full in this little is 2 hours</li><li>3-level LED power meter lets you know how your batteries are doing both in use and when charging</li><li>Internal lithium-ion battery is lighter than standard alkaline batteries and performs better in cold weather</li><li>Multi-faceted lens balances flood and spot lighting</li><li>Intuitive 2-button controls give you easy access to red lighting and flipping between spot and flood lighting</li><li>Night-vision friendly red light can be activated without cycling through white lighting</li><li>IP67 weatherproofing keeps you light shining bright in any weather you're willing to go out in</li><li>Adjustable headband is now made with recycled materials, including Repreve\u00ae fibres made from recycled plastic bottles</li><li>Lockout feature protects against accidental activations</li></ul>",
